This behavior is specification ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As related information ..&lt;br/&gt;
When specified the Non-existent package using &lt;tt&gt;@ComponentScan(basePackages)&lt;/tt&gt;, controller is not scanned.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think should be changed to the same behavior with &lt;tt&gt;@CompnentScan&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How do think ?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
